Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_thr

The transmit holding register is a write-only register that contains data to be transmitted on the serial output port (UART0/1_SOUT). Data can be written to MIO_UART(0..1)_THR any time that MIO_UART(0..1)_LSR[THRE] = 1.
